../org-agent-skills/org/org-level-skill-generation.log:547:├── SKILL.md (workflow + provider selection)
../org-agent-skills/org/org-level-skill-generation.log:579:- **Avoid deeply nested references** - Keep references one level deep from SKILL.md. All reference files should link directly from SKILL.md.
